pull.title: bip174: typo in some fixtures (using wrong magic prefix)
pull.body:
`bin2hex("psbt\xff") = 70736274ff`

A few of the invalid PSBT cases have been serialized using the wrong magic, but only in their base64 encodings.

ping @achow101

rename.from: bip174: bring hex encoding in line with base64 fixture
